        No sales call. No credit card. Just ForgeOS.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8 text-sm">
        Pro — $49/month. No sales call. Cancel anytime. First gate running in under 10 minutes. 14 days to decide.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="#trial"
